{
  "texts": [
    "All of the strategies significantly increased detection accuracy while remaining fast.",
    "DarkNet-53 served as the backbone for YOLOv3's extraction of picture characteristics, and logistics was employed in place of softmax for classification.",
    "The prediction was performed using the FPN network, and the previous frames were chosen using k-means clustering.",
    "In YOLOv3 (Redmon and Farhadi 2018), nine preceding frames were chosen, and three feature maps with various sensory fields were chosen to identify objects of various sizes.",
    "Ov4 (Bochkovskiy et al. 2020) introduced mosaic data enhancement on the input images."
  ]
}